{% extends "furniture.njk" %}

{% block content %}

    <h2>Three JS FPS experiment</h2>

    <p>An exploration of some of the features of the <a href="https://threejs.org/" target="_blank">ThreeJS</a> JavaScript library for 3D animation made in the style of a first person computer game. It features some basic controls and movement you might be familiar with as well a randomised forest and colourful cubes.
No credit can be taken for the 3D assets which were sourced online.
    </p>

