        </div>
    </div>

    <h3>Controls</h3>
    <ul>
        <li><strong>Play:</strong> Enter</li>
        <li><strong>Enter full screen:</strong> f1</li>
        <li><strong>Pause and exit full screen:</strong> esc</li>
        <li><strong>Movement:</strong> W A S D</li>
        <li><strong>Jump:</strong> Space</li>
        <li><strong>Cast ray / shoot:</strong> Right mouse button</li>
    </ul>

